            <p>本文用於記錄棺派粵語（20 世紀初）聲母“s”和“sh”對立時各所轄者，但不包括容易寫出漢字的，如「細小」「世上」等，此類字聲母大多可由普通話簡單推出。因此，本文主要關注一般不出現在書面語的詞彙。</p>
            <p>下表中，<b>記音</b>列可能有兩列，此時前一列是綜合音，可忽略；本文不寫出師韻 ii（/ɿ/）；<br>
            有些詞可能二聲母皆可，本文不置可否。</p>
            <p><b>字頭</b>列高亮者<b>不</b>代表本字或正字，而只是基於音、義來選出的相對較爲合理的字；併隨後的小號漢字可分別理解爲「優先字形」及「候選字形」；<br>
            <i>斜體者</i>代表該詞可能不出現在現代廣州話中，本文保留作爲參考；<br>
                以「Ｘ」表記的字頭表示本文未對該詞指定優先字形。</p>


<table border="1">
<caption>聲母 “s” 與 “sh” 轄字表</caption>
<tr><th style="width: 2.5em;">韻母</th>
    <th style="width: 2.5em;">聲調</th>
    <th style="width: 2.5em;">聲母</th>
    <th colspan="2">記音</th>
    <th style="width: 4em;">字頭</th>
    <th>釋義</th></tr>



    <tr><td rowspan="6">aa</td><td rowspan="3">1</td><td class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>saa1</td><td><span class='head'>卅</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>三十：年～晚</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3" class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>shaa1</td><td><span class='head'>沙</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔聲～〕嗓子沙啞</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shaa1</td><td><span class='head'>䖢</span><span class='sub'><small>𧋊</small></span></td><td class='mean'>〔𧌇～〕蛾類昆蟲</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td colspan='2'>shaa2</td><td><span class='head'>耍</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①遊戲，玩樂：『放假打算去邊啲去～』；②舞動，施展：～大牌</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">4</td><td class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>saa4</td><td><span class='head'>莎</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔pi1～〕意大利薄餅⟨英語：pizza⟩</td></tr>
<tr><td class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>shaa4?</td><td><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①〔～～滾〕浮躁，魯莽，亂來一通，好出風頭，不務正業四處玩；②〔～li1弄𧼩）莽撞，亂來</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="5">aai</td><td rowspan="2">1</td><td rowspan="3" class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>saai1</td><td><span class='head'>謕</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>譏笑，嘲諷：～檔(以言語拆臺)｜『佢論日～我冇文化』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>saai1</td><td><span class='head'>嘥</span><span class='sub'><small>㩄</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①浪費：～時間｜～壞(浪費)｜『冇食得咁多又要𢳂咁多，搞～啲穀米去』；②可惜：『差一隻數字就中一等獎喇，～哦』</td></tr>
<tr><td>3</td><td colspan='2'>saai3</td><td><span class='head'>晒</span><span class='sub'><small>嗮哂澌</small></span></td><td class='mean'>助詞，表全稱、程度、結果、完結等義，本或作「澌」：『多謝～！』｜『做～嘢正去耍』</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td rowspan="9" class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>shaai4</td><td><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔白～～〕苍白</td></tr>
<tr><td>5</td><td>shaai5</td><td><b>shaai2><br>saai2</b></td><td><span class='head'>舐</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>舔，大舌頭舔：『食完～乾净碗』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="4">aak</td><td rowspan="4">3</td><td colspan='2'>shaak3</td><td><i><span class='head'>溹</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>雨水飛濺：『雨從窗眼啲～落來』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shaak3</td><td><i><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>柵</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>〔肋～骨〕肋骨</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shaak3</td><td><i><span class='head'>索</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①喜歡，熱衷於；②胃口好：～食｜～飯</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shaak3</td><td><span class='head'>柵</span><span class='sub'><small>𤖴𢱢</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①量詞，（瓜果等）（人爲破開的）一瓣，一塊：『隻瓜捱破開兩～』；②量詞，一片區域：『啊～埞都在佢名下』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">aam</td><td>1</td><td colspan='2'>shaam1</td><td><span class='head'>衫</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>上衣，亦代指衣服：唥～｜～包(裝衣物的包袱)</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td colspan='2'>shaam4</td><td><i><span class='head'>饞</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①貪喫，專愛喫好的：嘴～；②貪，羨慕：眼～</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="5">aan</td><td>1</td><td colspan='2'>shaan1</td><td><span class='head'>閂</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>插閂關閉：～門｜～窗</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td rowspan="2" class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>saan2</td><td><span class='head'>散</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>零碎的：～錢</td></tr>
<tr><td>3</td><td colspan='2'>saan3</td><td><i><span class='head'>散</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>服藥後身體虛弱</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">4</td><td rowspan="5" class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>shaan4?</td><td><span class='head'>孱</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>軟弱：～仔</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shaan4</td><td><span class='head'>漦</span><span class='sub'><small>潺</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①黏液；②口水；③（碱水、粘液、湿物等）滑腻：～稠稠</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3">aang</td><td rowspan="3">2</td><td colspan='2'>shaang2</td><td><span class='head'>㨘</span><span class='sub'><small>省磢</small></span></td><td class='mean'>〔～鏡〕在照片或影片中顯得很漂亮、很上鏡</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shaang2</td><td><span class='head'>㨘</span><span class='sub'><small>省磢</small></span></td><td class='mean'>批评：『被老板～』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shaang2</td><td><span class='head'>㨘</span><span class='sub'><small>渻磢省</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①擦洗：～鑊；②訓斥：『捱老闆～』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="6">aap</td><td rowspan="5">3</td><td rowspan="4" class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>saap3</td><td><i><span class='head'>𫊷</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>蟑螂：騷～｜～蟲</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>saap3</td><td><i><span class='head'>喢</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>胡言：『最獳嗰種人喔，又冇識又要亂～』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>saap3</td><td><i><span class='head'>歃</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①理睬：『佢跟啲講了一日，其實冇有人～佢』；②[欽]〔～𫵱〕指對方胡言或想法不切實際</td></tr>
<tr><td>saap3?</td><td><b>saap3<br>saap6</b></td><td><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔𩰶～～〕粗糙</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2" class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>shaap3</td><td><span class='head'>唼</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔～氣〕慪氣，費心</td></tr>
<tr><td>6</td><td colspan='2'>shaap6</td><td><span class='head'>煠</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>一種烹飪方法，將食物置入熱水中煮</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">aat</td><td rowspan="2">3</td><td class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>saat3</td><td><i><span class='head'>撒</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①放開，散放：～手｜～尿；②受驚：『條蛇突然間飆出來，做我嚇～跳去』｜～醒；③散落：『米～得一地都係』｜～架(散架)；④播（種）</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="5" class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>shaat3</td><td><span class='head'>殺</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①贏錢，賺錢；②擅：～食；③答應條件，成交：『～你』；④〔～喉〕（酒、醋等）刺激喉嚨</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="9">aau</td><td>1</td><td colspan='2'>shaau1</td><td><span class='head'>筲</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①一種盛飯用的竹筐：～箕；②水桶：水～</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3">3</td><td colspan='2'>shaau3</td><td><i><span class='head'>捎</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>打：『一槌～过去』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shaau3</td><td><span class='head'>𪘞</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>門牙向外突出：～牙｜牙～～</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shaau3</td><td><span class='head'>潲</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①雨水溅洒：『雨往南～』；②泔水：猪～｜～水；③刷，涂抹：～油漆</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="4">4</td><td rowspan="3" class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>saau4</td><td><span class='head'>𢶠</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①掃，刮：『我一脚～過去』；②掃蕩：『～齊啲菜去』；③大口地喫</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>saau4</td><td><span class='head'>𡮦</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>見𤎤𡮦</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>saau4</td><td><span class='head'>睄</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>視線快速掃過：『一眼～過去，教室冇有幾隻人』｜～來～去</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="6" class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>shaau4?</td><td><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>隨手拿取，同“𢶌shaa1”</td></tr>
<tr><td>6</td><td colspan='2'>shaau6</td><td><i><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>丟，扔</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="7">ai</td><td rowspan="2">1</td><td colspan='2'>shai1</td><td><span class='head'>簁</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>同篩，見俹簁</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shai1</td><td><span class='head'>篩</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>用篩子過：～米</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">2</td><td colspan='2'>shai2</td><td><i><span class='head'>駛</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>御駛（牲畜）：～牛｜～牛耙田</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shai2</td><td><span class='head'>使</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①用：～力｜～嘢；②派，差譴：『老乸經常～我去買嘢』；③需要（用於否定、疑問）：『唔～落去咁早』；④花費：～錢｜『整份表～了我好耐』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">3</td><td rowspan="6" class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>sai3</td><td><span class='head'>細</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>小</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>sai3</td><td><span class='head'>細</span><span class='sub'><small>世</small></span></td><td class='mean'>〔老～〕①老闆，舊稱商店主人，今泛指工商企業、公司行號的產權所有人；②直屬上司；③（本科生或研究生的）指導老師，指導教授；④對顧客的不正式但尊敬的稱呼</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td colspan='2'>sai4?</td><td><span class='head'>噬</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>咬，吞：『着狗～了一口』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3">ak</td><td rowspan="2">1</td><td colspan='2'>sak1</td><td><i><span class='head'>噻</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①不定指，有的，某一：～日｜『～輪冇上課都冇問題』；②〔一～𧦠〕一不留神：『～冇記得帶遮出屋』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>sak1</td><td><span class='head'>息</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'><白>孫之子，重孫，曾孫：孫孫～～</td></tr>
<tr><td>6</td><td colspan='2'>sak6</td><td><i><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>瞔</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>〔醒～〕機靈</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">am</td><td>1</td><td class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>sham1</td><td><span class='head'>深</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①從表面到底或從外面到裡面距離大，與“淺”相對：『部車停得夠～』；②玄妙，深奧：『條題好～』｜～筆字</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>sam2</td><td><i><span class='head'>𥊀</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>理睬：『佢又冇～我』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="4">an</td><td>3</td><td class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>shan3</td><td><span class='head'>呻</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①〔～聲〕無病呻吟；②抱怨：『佢成日～佢俾阿媽打』</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>san4</td><td><i><span class='head'>𢲜</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>顫抖⟨壯語：saenz⟩</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">5</td><td rowspan="2" class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>shan5</td><td><span class='head'>順</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>（薯、芋等）脆生，不鬆軟：～水(脆而不軟糯)</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shan5</td><td><span class='head'>腎</span><span class='sub'><small>脤</small></span></td><td class='mean'>傻：～仔</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">ang</td><td>3</td><td rowspan="3" class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>sang3</td><td><span class='head'>擤</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>用氣排出鼻：～鼻涕</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td colspan='2'>sang4</td><td><i><span class='head'>傖</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>傻貌：笑～～｜懵～～｜戇～～</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="4">ap</td><td rowspan="3">1</td><td colspan='2'>sap1</td><td><span class='head'>漝</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>零碎的，零散的：～碎(零碎、瑣碎)</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2" class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>shap1</td><td><span class='head'>溼</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>沾水或含水多：～浡浡(潮溼)</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>shap1</td><td><i><span class='head'>溼</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>避諱詞，避“肝”“竿”等：豬～｜擔～</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td rowspan="2" class="B">s</td><td colspan='2'>sap4</td><td><i><span class='head'>𰈄</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>大口吞：『～佢一口』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="4">at</td><td rowspan="2">1</td><td colspan='2'>sat1</td><td><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>恤[⿰冫戌]悉</small></span></td><td class='mean'>理睬（多用於熟人之間）⟨壯語：swt⟩：『冇～你啦』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3" class="A">sh</td><td colspan='2'>shat1</td><td><span class='head'>蝨</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>無翅小型體外寄生蟲統稱，吸血爲生，能傳染疾病：頭～｜～乸</td></tr>
